Titolo: The Legend of Sword and Fairy 6

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: The Legend of Sword and Fairy 6 is a role-playing game developed by Softstar Technology (Beijing) Co.,Ltd. It is the eighth installment in The Legend of Sword and Fairy (or Chinese Paladin) video game series, preceded by Chinese Paladin 5 Prequel and its story is set years after the events of The Legend of Sword and Fairy 5. The game incorporates elements of wuxia, shenmo and fantasy. It is scheduled to released for Xbox One.